<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 02 Jan 2025 06:20:07 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>随着竞争加剧，苹果在中国提供 iPhone 折扣</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/apple-offers-iphone-discounts-china-competition-intensifies-2025-01-02/</link><description>苹果在中国为其最新款 iPhone 机型提供罕见的高达 500 元人民币（合 68.50 美元）的折扣，这家美国科技巨头正在采取行动，抵御来自华为等国内竞争对手日益激烈的竞争，以捍卫自己的市场份额。</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Jan 2025 05:57:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/apple-offers-iphone-discounts-china-competition-intensifies-2025-01-02/</guid></item><item><title>中国卫健委将缩小精神卫生服务差距</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-health-commission-narrow-gaps-mental-health-services-2025-01-02/</link><description>中国国家卫生健康委员会表示，随着当局努力解决越来越多的心理健康问题，特别是儿童和青少年的心理健康问题，将在2025年至2027年期间解决心理健康服务方面的差距。</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Jan 2025 05:57:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-health-commission-narrow-gaps-mental-health-services-2025-01-02/</guid></item><item><title>台湾报道新年首次中国“战斗巡逻”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-reports-first-chinese-combat-patrol-new-year-2025-01-02/</link><description>在台湾总统赖清德再次表示愿意与北京对话后，台湾国防部周四表示，中国战机和军舰已进行新年首次环岛“战斗巡逻”。</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Jan 2025 05:28:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-reports-first-chinese-combat-patrol-new-year-2025-01-02/</guid></item><item><title>特朗普2.0风险加大，亚洲工厂2024年末表现疲软</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asias-factories-end-2024-weak-footing-trump-20-risks-mount-2025-01-02/</link><description>亚洲工厂强国在 2024 年结束时表现疲软，因为唐纳德·特朗普连任总统导致贸易风险不断加大，加上中国经济复苏脆弱，新年预期恶化。</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Jan 2025 03:28:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asias-factories-end-2024-weak-footing-trump-20-risks-mount-2025-01-02/</guid></item><item><title>财新PMI显示中国工厂活动增长放缓</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/growth-chinas-factory-activity-slows-caixin-pmi-shows-2025-01-02/</link><description>周四的一项私营部门调查显示，由于对贸易前景的担忧导致出口订单下降，整体销售受到抑制，中国12月份工厂活动有所增长，但增速低于预期。</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Jan 2025 01:47:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/growth-chinas-factory-activity-slows-caixin-pmi-shows-2025-01-02/</guid></item><item><title>《华盛顿邮报》称中国对美国财政部的黑客攻击违反了制裁办公室</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/cybersecurity/us-treasurys-sanctions-office-hacked-by-chinese-government-washington-post-2025-01-02/</link><description>据《华盛顿邮报》周三报道，中国政府黑客入侵了负责管理经济制裁的美国财政部办公室，并确定了本周早些时候披露的财政部网络攻击目标。</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Jan 2025 00:01:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/cybersecurity/us-treasurys-sanctions-office-hacked-by-chinese-government-washington-post-2025-01-02/</guid></item><item><title>普京命令俄罗斯政府和顶级银行与中国发展人工智能合作</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/putin-orders-russian-government-top-bank-develop-ai-cooperation-with-china-2025-01-01/</link><description>俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京已命令俄罗斯政府和该国最大的银行俄罗斯联邦储蓄银行与中国在人工智能领域建立合作。</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 Jan 2025 13:07:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/putin-orders-russian-government-top-bank-develop-ai-cooperation-with-china-2025-01-01/</guid></item><item><title>2024年，中国迎来几十年来最热的一年，再次打破纪录</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/2024-china-saw-warmest-year-decades-breaking-records-yet-again-2025-01-01/</link><description>中国气象数据显示，2024年是该国自六十多年前有可比记录以来最热的一年，这是连续第二年打破里程碑。</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 Jan 2025 13:04:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/2024-china-saw-warmest-year-decades-breaking-records-yet-again-2025-01-01/</guid></item><item><title>中国阿里巴巴将以16亿美元将高鑫零售股份出售给DCP</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/chinas-alibaba-sell-sun-art-stake-dcp-16-billion-2025-01-01/</link><description>中国阿里巴巴集团控股有限公司周三表示，已同意以 122.98 亿港元（15.8 亿美元）的价格将其在连锁超市高鑫零售集团的多数股权出售给中国私募股权公司 DCP Capital。</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 Jan 2025 12:12:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/chinas-alibaba-sell-sun-art-stake-dcp-16-billion-2025-01-01/</guid></item><item><title>澳门 2024 年赌场收入高于官方预期，但低于大流行前的水平</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/macau-2024-casino-revenues-top-official-estimate-below-pre-pandemic-levels-2025-01-01/</link><description>全球最大的博彩中心澳门的赌场收入在 2024 年猛增近四分之一，但仍低于大流行前的水平，突显这个前葡萄牙殖民地需要实现经济多元化。</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 Jan 2025 10:26:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/macau-2024-casino-revenues-top-official-estimate-below-pre-pandemic-levels-2025-01-01/</guid></item><item><title>朝中社称，朝鲜金正恩出席新年庆祝活动并收到中国习近平的贺卡</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-koreas-kim-jong-un-attends-new-years-celebrations-with-daughter-kcna-2025-01-01/</link><description>据官方媒体朝中社周三报道，朝鲜领导人金正恩和他的女儿珠爱参加了新年庆祝活动，包括烟花和冰舞表演。</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 Jan 2025 10:25:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-koreas-kim-jong-un-attends-new-years-celebrations-with-daughter-kcna-2025-01-01/</guid></item><item><title>调查显示中国12月新房价格涨幅略快</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-december-new-home-prices-rise-touch-faster-survey-shows-2025-01-01/</link><description>周三的一项私人调查显示，12月份中国新房价格上涨速度略快，受危机打击的房地产行业在政府一系列支持性政策的推动下艰难寻找底部。</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 Jan 2025 02:54:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-december-new-home-prices-rise-touch-faster-survey-shows-2025-01-01/</guid></item><item><title>行业低迷加深，中国2024票房收入暴跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/media-telecom/china-2024-box-office-revenue-plunges-industry-downturn-deepens-2025-01-01/</link><description>周三官方数据显示，中国2024年票房收入同比下降近四分之一，对尚未从疫情中完全恢复的国内电影业造成打击。</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 Jan 2025 02:35:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/media-telecom/china-2024-box-office-revenue-plunges-industry-downturn-deepens-2025-01-01/</guid></item><item><title>台湾总统希望与中国交流，但认为缺乏善意</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-president-says-he-welcomes-exchanges-with-china-2025-01-01/</link><description>台湾总统赖清德周三表示，他欢迎与中国进行平等、有尊严、健康和有序的交流，但他想知道北京是否有善意，因为他所说的北京对旅游业等简单的事情进行了封锁。</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 Jan 2025 01:09:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-president-says-he-welcomes-exchanges-with-china-2025-01-01/</guid></item><item><title>墨西哥公布新关税，Shein、Temu 等热门电子零售商可能成为瞄准目标</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/mexico-unveils-new-tariffs-popular-e-tailers-like-shein-temu-may-be-crosshairs-2024-12-31/</link><description>墨西哥税务机关 SAT 周二发布了新关税，称新关税将加强对来自亚洲的商品的监管，这一措施可能会影响 Shein 和 Temu 等热门在线零售商。</description><pubDate>Tue, 31 Dec 2024 19:34:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/mexico-unveils-new-tariffs-popular-e-tailers-like-shein-temu-may-be-crosshairs-2024-12-31/</guid></item></channel></rss>